PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?dog ?dogLabel ?birth ?death ?yearsDiff ?ageYears WHERE {
  ?dog wdt:P31 wd:Q144 .
  ?dog wdt:P569 ?birth .
  ?dog wdt:P570 ?death .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?dog rdfs:label ?dogLabel FILTER ( LANG( ?dogLabel ) = "en" )
  }
  BIND( ( YEAR( ?death ) - YEAR( ?birth ) ) AS ?yearsDiff ) BIND( IF( ( MONTH( ?death ) < MONTH( ?birth ) ) || ( MONTH( ?death ) = MONTH( ?birth ) && DAY( ?death ) < DAY( ?birth ) ) , ( ?yearsDiff - 1 ) , ?yearsDiff ) AS ?ageYears )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?ageYears )
OFFSET 1
LIMIT 1

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?film ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?film wdt:P57 wd:Q8006 .
  ?film wdt:P31 ?type .
  ?type wdt:P279 * wd:Q11424 .
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
SELECT ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?year ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  wd:Q169452 p:P166 ?s1 .
  ?s1 ps:P166 wd:Q674359 .
  ?s1 pq:P585 ?date1 .
  wd:Q25369 p:P166 ?s2 .
  ?s2 ps:P166 wd:Q674359 .
  ?s2 pq:P585 ?date2 .
  BIND( YEAR( ?date1 ) AS ?year1 ) BIND( YEAR( ?date2 ) AS ?year2 ) FILTER ( ?year1 = ?year2 ) BIND( ?year1 AS ?year )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q794 wdt:P36 ?capitalIran .
  wd:Q183 wdt:P36 ?capitalGermany .
  ?capitalIran wdt:P1082 ?popIran .
  ?capitalGermany wdt:P1082 ?popGermany .
  FILTER ( ?popIran > ?popGermany )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q183 wdt:P2046 ?areaDE .
  wd:Q36 wdt:P2046 ?areaPL .
  FILTER ( ?areaDE > ?areaPL )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
ASK {
  ?place wdt:P17 wd:Q39 ; wdt:P625 ?loc .
  BIND( STR( ?loc ) AS ?locs ) BIND( REPLACE( ?locs , "(?i)^POINT\\(" , "" ) AS ?no1 ) BIND( REPLACE( ?no1 , "\\)$" , "" ) AS ?nos ) BIND( STRAFTER( ?nos , " " ) AS ?latstr ) BIND( xsd:double ( ?latstr ) AS ?lat ) FILTER ( ?lat > 47.8 )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?work ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?work wdt:P50 wd:Q30875 .
  FILTER ( ?work != wd:Q82464 ) .
  ?work wdt:P31 ?class .
  ?class wdt:P279 * wd:Q7725634 .
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?film ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?film wdt:P57 wd:Q42574 .
  ?film wdt:P31 / wdt:P279 * wd:Q11424 .
  ?film wdt:P577 ?date .
  FILTER ( ?date < "2010-01-01T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime )
}

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/>
SELECT ?generation ?birthStart ?birthEnd ?ageMin ?ageMax WHERE {
  BIND( wd:Q3044693 AS ?generation ) ?generation schema:description ?desc .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?desc ) = "en" ) BIND( STR( ?desc ) AS ?s ) BIND( STRAFTER( ?s , "born from " ) AS ?afterstart ) BIND( STRBEFORE( ?afterstart , " to " ) AS ?birthStartStr ) BIND( STRAFTER( ?afterstart , " to " ) AS ?afterend ) BIND( STRBEFORE( CONCAT ( ?afterend , " " ) , " " ) AS ?birthEndStr ) BIND( xsd:integer ( REPLACE( ?birthStartStr , "\\D" , "" ) ) AS ?birthStart ) BIND( xsd:integer ( REPLACE( ?birthEndStr , "\\D" , "" ) ) AS ?birthEnd ) BIND( ( 2025 - ?birthEnd - 1 ) AS ?ageMin ) BIND( ( 2025 - ?birthStart ) AS ?ageMax )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q860580 wdt:P112 ?f1 .
  wd:Q860580 wdt:P112 ?f2 .
  FILTER ( ?f1 != ?f2 ) .
  ?f1 wdt:P69 ?uni .
  ?f2 wdt:P69 ?uni .
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q510 wdt:P1589 ?deep .
  ?deep wdt:P2044 ?deep_elev .
  wd:Q513 wdt:P2044 ?eve_elev .
  FILTER ( ( - ?deep_elev ) > ?eve_elev )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?occ ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?winner wdt:P166 wd:Q37922 .
  ?winner wdt:P31 wd:Q5 .
  ?winner wdt:P26 ?spouse .
  ?spouse wdt:P106 ?occ .
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?female ) AS ?womenCount ) ( GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT ?female ; separator = "|" ) AS ?femaleFounders ) WHERE {
  wd:Q152778 wdt:P112 ?founder .
  ?founder wdt:P21 wd:Q6581072 .
  BIND( ?founder AS ?female )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q567 wdt:P569 ?dob1 .
  wd:Q9545 wdt:P569 ?dob2 .
  BIND( SUBSTR( STR( ?dob1 ) , 1 , 4 ) AS ?y1 ) BIND( SUBSTR( STR( ?dob2 ) , 1 , 4 ) AS ?y2 ) FILTER ( ?y1 = ?y2 )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
ASK {
  wd:Q1650 wdt:P2043 ?weser_len .
  wd:Q584 wdt:P2043 ?rhine_len .
  FILTER ( ?weser_len > ?rhine_len )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q2926117 wdt:P19 ?place1 .
  wd:Q87192979 wdt:P19 ?place2 .
  ?place1 wdt:P131 * ?state .
  ?place2 wdt:P131 * ?state .
  ?state wdt:P31 wd:Q35657 .
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
SELECT ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?person ) AS ?count ) ( GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT STR( ?person ) ; separator = ", " ) AS ?persons ) WHERE {
  ?person p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q218295 .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?start .
  FILTER ( ?start > "1990-12-31T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?death ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?work ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  wd:Q7245 wdt:P570 ?death .
  ?work wdt:P50 wd:Q7245 .
  ?work wdt:P31 / wdt:P279 * wd:Q7725634 .
}
